name: Jaime L. Garcia
text: At any rate, I bought it on semi-sale from Fully Booked, so if you still want to buy it when I get back sometime in 3-6 months, I'll sell it to you for relatively cheap (like 50% off) - like the cards, I just want it to have a good home.
